description:
In this video, I'm sharing my version of "The Way of the Cross" by Karaoke. This gospel karaoke song is sure to bring a tear to your eye as you belt out the lyrics.
If you're looking for a way to worship the Lord in a unique and special way, then you need to check out this gospel karaoke video! This song is sure to touch your heart and bring you closer to God. Birthing this song was a journey of self-discovery for me and I'm hopeful that it will be for you too.

First Line : I must needs go home by the way of the cross
Title : The Way of the Cross Leads Home
Author : Jessie Brown Pounds (1906)'
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube channel
